Invoke deposit and withdraw functions[​](https://docs-v2.mantle.xyz/devs/dev-guides/how-to/bridge-mnt#invoke-deposit-and-withdraw-functions)

We write a `main()` where we call the functions to perform configuration, deposit, and withdraw operations.

